### 5. `evidence` Field Type Inconsistency in Proposals

`protocol.json` requires `evidence` but does not specify its type. In `proposals.jsonl`:
- commander-001 (line 1): array of strings ✓
- commander-003 (line 2): plain string — inconsistent
- commander-005 (line 3): array of strings ✓
- commander-002 (line 4): array of strings ✓

The monitor and any synthesis consumer that expects a uniform type will fail silently on commander-003's record. Reviews omit `evidence` entirely, making this a three-way inconsistency across event types.

