**File:** `skills/SKILL.md` (no collab matches found)

The orchestrator skill that generates task manifests and drives workflow has zero collab references. Tasks generated via the skill will not embed collab paths into manifests. This creates the F-01 gap structurally.

**Fix:** Add a collab-bus awareness section to SKILL.md that copies the resolved `collab` dict into every metaswarm task manifest it creates.

