## 8. Ordering Requirements Summary

Per `agents/stampede-commander.agent.md` and observed `child-agents.jsonl` records:

```
Correct per-child sequence:
  1. launch_requested  (before agent spawns)
  2. launch_started    (immediately after spawn; update swarm-state.json atomically)
  3. completed         (after result received; include atom_id if worker)

Collab bus sequence (protocol.json):
  propose → peer_review → improve → consensus → broadcast → adopt
```

**Violations found:** commander-002 starts with `launch_started`+`completed` at identical timestamps, skipping `launch_requested`; later entries switch to non-standard event names (`task_complete`, `squad_complete`).

