### BUG-14: No validation mechanism exists anywhere
**Severity: High (operational)**

`protocol.json` is read by no code. `stampede-monitor.sh` counts ledger lines (`wc -l`) but never parses field presence or types. The smoke test (`tests/smoke-test.sh`) validates fleet.json and swarm-state.json structure but does not validate any JSONL ledger records. The depth-guard lint (`tests/depth-guard-lint.sh`) checks agent markdown text only. There is no CI step, no runtime validator, and no post-run check that reads `required_fields` from `protocol.json` and validates it against any ledger record.

